entity_resolver.parser package¶

Contains data parser classes.

This package contains parser classes in entity_resolver.parser.graph_parser module and entity_resolver.parser.ground_truth_parser module. It is created for import convenience similar to entity_resolver package. For details, please follow the submodule links to their documentation pages.
